  <p>
    This December, ISJ's campus became a place of magic. Twinkling lights wound through the school, live music filled the air, and student-made decorations hung beautifully from every corner. The ISJ Christmas Fair returned to delight the community, and it delivered on every count.
  </p>

  <p>
    A special guest appearance from Santa himself was a moment that will stay with the youngest members of the ISJ family for a long time to come.
  </p>

  <h2>The Parents' Circle</h2>

  <p>
    None of it would have been possible without the ISJ Parents' Circle. Their dedication, creativity, and countless hours of work behind the scenes brought the Christmas Fair to life. The school is genuinely grateful for everything they do, not just at Christmas but throughout the year. The fair is a testament to what a committed parent community can achieve.
  </p>

  <h2>The Christmas Raffle</h2>

  <p>
    The much-loved annual Christmas raffle was another highlight of the day. Exceptional prizes generated real excitement, and the school extends its thanks to all of the generous prize sponsors whose donations made the raffle such a success.
  </p>

  <h2>What Makes ISJ Special</h2>

  <p>
    Events like the Christmas Fair are more than just a celebration. They are a reflection of the warmth and vibrancy of the ISJ community. For families already part of the school, the Fair is a chance to connect, celebrate, and feel proud of the community they have chosen. For families considering ISJ, it offers a glimpse of the spirit that runs through everything the school does.
  </p>

</ArticleLayout>
